 />\n麻煩各位聽日以武抗暴都要保持理性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:49:16.000Z","msg":"不如話有心人（e.g.廢老kol、Carrie個姐姐）唔想單野平熄，不斷撥火。"},{"pid":"413c1ac623768ce5667a72d0309ace6ddc0b508a","tid":1663361,"uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"競猜埋tim呀洗唔洗比個獎你呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"6c06ca0f79d47bc4e7a8c91670d23ecb20827f17","tid":1663361,"uid":57614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:12:18.000Z","msg":"charge毆鬥"},{"pid":"c1789a015b984121794ffc6da8ea5526ffc68c7c","tid":1663361,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce976f8a852d8dd1101ac00acad80148fa3c35d","tid":1663361,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:56:34.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"7a569ef440198ad49f060c2d893a5ab11879db61","tid":1663361,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}